quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  48,29,"Muhammdu ko Nulaa…óo Allah. Won'…óu…ďe e makko …ďeen ko √Īaa…óu…ďe e yeddu…ďe …ďeen, yurmondir…ďe hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. A yi'at …ďe hi…ďe ru∆ī∆īa, hi…ďe cujja, hi…ďe …óa…ď…ďira Allah …ďural e welayee. Ma'andeeji ma…ď…ďe …óin no ka j'eece ma…ď…ďe batte cujjugol ngol. Ko …óuum woni ko …ďe ciforaa ka Tawreeta. No …ďe ciforaa ka Linjiila kan, ko wano remuru yaltingu pu…ói mayru, ngu …ďanngini …ói, …ói tekki, …ói fotondiri e binndeeje majji, hara …óuum no haawna remoo…ďe, fii no [Allah] tikkinira …ďe yeddu…ďe …ďen. Allah fodii e ma…ď…ďe …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īu…ói …óin, haforanal e njo…ďdi mawnundi."
  49,1,"Eey mon yo …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe ! wota on adito ye'eso Allah e Nulaa…óo makko on. Hulee Allah. Pellet, Allah ko Nanoowo, Ji'oowo."
  49,2,"Eey mon yo …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe ! wota on toownu hitooji mon e dow hito Annabaajo on, wota on ewnor mo kadi konngol, wano no yoga mon ewnorta yoga, sakko golle mon …óen mbonata, hara on so'aa-anndude."
  49,3,"Pellet, …ďeen joltinoo…ďe hotooji ma…ď…ďe …óin ka Nulaa…óo Allah on, ko …ďen ngoni …ďe Alla jarabii …ďer…óe mum …óen gooŇč…óal. Hino woodani …ďe haforanal e njo…ďdi mawndi."
  49,4,"Pellet, …ďeen …ďe no noddire ka …ďaawo cuu…ói, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe, wonaa haqqiloo…ďe."